public void symbolNameChanged(AgentNameEvent e)
Handles a change in the panel's symbol-name. This method changes the frame's title to me the possibly revised display name. Subclasses may need to take additional steps.

makeDomainEditor

public InternalDomainEditor makeDomainEditor(IXAgent agent,
                                             Domain dom)
Constructs the domain editor for this panel. If a domain-editor-class parameter has been specified, its value is taken as the name of a class that implements the InternalDomainEditor interface and supplies an (IXAgent, Domain) constructor. If an exception is thrown when that constructor is called, or if no class parameter was specified, a default class is instantiated instead.
